Q11.15: The address I have provided is for one of the four parcels I own, but I have provided answers based on a balance of the verying considerations.  On one parcel I would probably accept $25/ha because it is not very accessible and of limited agricultural value.  On another with better pasture and access around $75 would be required.  The other two parcels are probably a bit of both and around $50 is reasonable to replace current earning potential.  I applied $50 as an average across all for parcels (held in two separate holdings, one on Reedy Creek Road Mole River, the other on the Bruxner Highway, Dumaresq Valley).
